Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:56.38,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(721,615)}The Power of Uchiha\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have different bonds...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonds of hatred with\Nmy older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Numerous bonds...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,mislead oneself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and weaken\Nthe most important desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and cherished memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you finally opened\N{\i1}your eyes...Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't even have parents\N{\i1}or siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you know about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've been alone from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do {\i0}you{\i1} know\N{\i1}about me?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's having the bond\N{\i1}that makes it painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've no idea what it's like...\N{\i1}to lose that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know about having\N{\i1}real parents or siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why, Naruto...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do you go so far for me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To me, it's a bond...I've finally\N{\i1}been able to establish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I'll stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't turn back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll just break\N{\i1}that bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you kill me\Nback then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that could\Nbreak our bond, Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason's simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I couldn't break\Nthe bond with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who might be able to use the same\N{\i1}Mangekyo Sharingan as mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, there's a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}your closest friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just irritating to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Obtaining power based on\Nthe method he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not necessary\Nto explain that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What I can say to you is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Rasengan!\N- {\i1}Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only alive\Nbecause of my passing whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't it your dream\Nto become the Hokage...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had the time\Nto be chasing after me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you should've spent that time\Ntraining or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sasuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And so this time around...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll lose your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,because of my passing whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No way can a guy who can't\Neven save one friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,become the Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That manner of defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chidori Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's unleashing Chidori\N{\i1}from his entire body...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll have to wait a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time, I promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't be a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll stop Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with my own power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those eyes.\N{\i1}This guy's bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That manner of defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This Snake Sword of mine\Nis somewhat special, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body is getting numb...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he sending a Chidori\Nthrough the blade...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it... It paralyzes you\N{\i1}with numbness after cutting...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}on top of increasing the cutting quality\N{\i1}to the extreme...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears...\Nthings have gotten interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance, Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Show him...our...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you hesitate...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You need my power, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you want to kill...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...come out anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need anything like\Nyour power anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was the one\Nwho had the nerve...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask for my help\Nat every opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know that you can't\Ndo anything on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Break the Seal completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll grant you all of my powers\Nif you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...\NSo you're an Uchiha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how you've grown...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is\Nyour unknown power, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd have something like this\Ninside of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To think you'd become able\Nto see me within Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That dreadful Sharingan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the power of\Nthe cursed clan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems this isn't the first time\Nyou've seen the Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you must be\Nthe Nine-Tailed Fox, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That vision, and Chakra\Nmore ominous than mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... Madara Uchiha from olden times...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uchiha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell if I know...that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you would go so far as\Nto suppress my power...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But let me tell you...one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...kill...Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,regret...it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wood Style: Domed Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...
